  "ComponentID": "W25Q128JV",
  "ComponentType": "Serial NOR Flash Memory (SPI/Dual/Quad I/O)",
  "Description": "The W25Q128JV is a 3V, 128M-bit (16MB) serial flash memory designed for systems with constrained space, pin count, and power. It supports standard SPI, Dual SPI, and Quad SPI interfaces, enabling high-speed data transfer with clock frequencies up to 133MHz, equivalent to 266MHz (Dual I/O) and 532MHz (Quad I/O) effective rates. Organized into 65,536 pages of 256 bytes each, it features flexible erase capabilities: 4KB sectors, 32KB blocks, 64KB blocks, or full-chip erase. It operates from 2.7V to 3.6V with ultra-low power-down current and includes advanced features like execute-in-place (XIP), software/hardware reset, and configurable write protection.",
